                <div class="feature-icon">üî¨</div>
                <h3>Science-Backed Analysis</h3>
                <p>We break down pheromone compounds and explain what each ingredient actually does.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="feature-icon">üö´</div>
                <h3>Zero Affiliate Bias</h3>
                <p>Not affiliated with any brand. We buy and test products ourselves.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="feature-icon">üìä</div>
                <h3>Comparison Tools</h3>
                <p>Compare products side-by-side by price, strength, compounds, and user ratings.</p>
